            <p class="mb-6">
                Today, Recipe Haven serves thousands of home cooks who, like us, believe that food should bring us together, not drive us apart. We're not backed by venture capital or major corporations. We're sustained by people who believe in what we're doing.
            </p>

            <p class="mb-6">
                That cracked tablet still sits on my desk—a battle scar from the day we decided to reclaim cooking from those who had weaponized it against us. It reminds me daily of what we're fighting for: the simple dignity of making a meal without a fight.
            </p>

            <blockquote class="bg-soft-pink bg-opacity-20 border-l-4 border-deep-rose p-4 italic my-8">
                "We believe that every recipe has a soul—an essence that connects generations, cultures, and hearts. That soul was being suffocated. We're here to set it free again."
            </blockquote>

            <p class="mb-8">
                Thank you for being part of our sanctuary. Every time you use a recipe from our site, you're helping prove that there's a better way—that we don't have to accept digital violence as the price of making dinner.
            </p>

